DESCRIPTION:Join SEIU Local 083 at noon in Memorial Union room 215. The Memorial Union double-booked our usual MU 211 room and found this alternate space. TOGO'S sandwiches will be provided. We will talk through the new phase of bargaining\, member readiness\, and how higher ed works because we work. Zoom details are coming shortly.
